()ComplianceReport kya hai?
--🔷 🧠 ComplianceReport kya hai?
👉 ComplianceReport = ek report jo batata hai ki system rules/policies follow ho rahe hain ya nahi
📌 Simple line:-
👉 “Kis user ne kya violation kiya, kaun compliant hai, kaun nahi”

🔷 🔥 Ye kya karta hai?
✅ 1. Policy violations dikhata hai,
👉 Example:-
User ke paas 2 conflicting roles (SoD violation)
Unauthorized access

✅ 2. Audit ke liye use hota hai,
👉 Companies ko proof chahiye hota hai:-
kis user ke paas kya access hai
kisne approve kiya

✅ 3. Risk identify karta hai,
👉 High risk users detect karta hai.

✅ 4. Certification support karta hai,
👉 Certification campaign me use hota hai.

🔷 🔥 Real Life Example:-
💻 Maan le:-
Rule: “User ek hi time pe Finance + Admin role nahi rakh sakta”
👉 Agar kisi ke paas dono hai ❌
➡️ ComplianceReport me dikhega
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
🔷 🔥 ComplianceReport ke andar kya hota hai?
👉 Ye ek structured report hota hai jisme:-
🔹 1. Identity Info:-
user name
email
department

🔹 2. Violations:-
kaunsa rule break hua
kis role/access ki wajah se

🔹 3. Policy Name:-
kaunsi policy violate hui

🔹 4. Risk Score:-
low / medium / high

🔹 5. Access Details:-
kaunse applications ka access hai

🔹 6. Approval Info:-
kisne approve kiya
kab approve hua

🔹 7. Timestamp:-
kab violation detect hua.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
🔷 🔥 Types of Compliance Reports:-
✅ 1. Policy Violation Report:-
👉 SoD violations

✅ 2. Access Review Report:-
👉 kis user ke paas kya access hai

✅ 3. Audit Report:-
👉 historical logs

✅ 4. Risk Report:-
👉 high risk identities
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
🔷 🔥 Flow me kaise use hota hai?
👉 Flow:-
Policies define hoti hain
System evaluate karta hai
Violations detect hote hain
ComplianceReport generate hota hai
Auditor / Admin check karta hai.
---------------------------------------------------
🔷 🔥 DB me store hota hai kya?
👉 ✅ Haan bhai, indirectly store hota hai

📍 Important Tables:-
🔸 spt_identity
👉 user data

🔸 spt_policy_violation
👉 violations store hote hain 🔥

🔸 spt_certification
👉 certification data

🔸 spt_audit_event
👉 audit logs
-----------------------------------------------------------
